    <span>Premium Grooming</span><span class="dot">✦</span>
    <span>Classic Cuts</span><span class="dot">✦</span>
    <span>Hot Towel Shaves</span><span class="dot">✦</span>
    <span>Beard Sculpting</span><span class="dot">✦</span>
    <span>Scalp Treatments</span><span class="dot">✦</span>
